title: Mini-Ep 269: Most Likely To Smash The Patriarchy
itunes:title: Mini-Ep 269: Most Likely To Smash The Patriarchy
description:
Kate and Doree just try to stay afloat while struggling with a possible case of Omicron and a twisted ankle. Then, listeners ask for sustainable bathroom recs, wonder how everyone else is deciding when to start a family, and fight back against a world telling women not to complain.
